#: ../../../index.rst:7
msgid "Vyper"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:9
msgid ""
"Vyper is a Pythonic smart contract language that compiles to `Ethereum "
"Virtual Machine (EVM) <https://ethereum.org/learn/#ethereum-basics>`_ "
"bytecode. It prioritises **security**, **auditability**, and **simplicity**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:15
msgid "Principles"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:17
msgid ""
"**Security**: Building secure smart contracts should be natural, not an "
"uphill battle."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:18
msgid ""
"**Simplicity**: Both the language and compiler should be easy to understand."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:19
msgid ""
"**Auditability**: Code should be maximally human-readable. Simplicity for "
"the reader matters more than convenience for the writer."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:22
msgid "Key Features"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:24
msgid "**Safety by default**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:26
msgid "Bounds and overflow checking on array accesses and arithmetic"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:27
msgid ""
"Reentrancy protection via the ``@nonreentrant`` decorator (see :ref:`control-"
"structures`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:28
msgid "Strong typing with explicit :ref:`type conversions <type_conversions>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:30
msgid "**Predictable execution**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:32
msgid ""
"Decidable gas consumption: every function call has a calculable upper bound"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:33
msgid "Bounded loops only (compile-time maximum iterations)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:34
msgid "No recursion: execution flow is structurally decreasing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:36
msgid "**Clean code reuse**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:38
msgid ":ref:`Module imports <modules>` instead of class inheritance"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:39
msgid ""
"Explicit ``extcall`` and ``staticcall`` keywords for external contract "
"interactions"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:40
msgid ""
"Support for :ref:`pure functions <function-mutability>` that cannot modify "
"state"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:43
msgid "Compiler-Enforced Security"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../index.rst:45
msgid ""
"Vyper eliminates entire vulnerability classes by excluding features that "
"enable dangerous patterns:"
